      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  EntityBrokerManagerImpl
      This is the internal service for handling entities, most of the work done by entity broker is handled here
      This should be used in preference to the EntityBroker directly by implementation classes that are part of the EntityBroker system, rather than the user-facing EntityBroker directly.
